== Re-license history ==

Tessera released versions through and including v0.11.0 under the
GNU Affero General Public License, Version 3.0 or later
(AGPL-3.0-or-later). The full text of that license is preserved
in the file LICENSE-AGPL-historical for reference.

Effective with the v0.11.1 release on 2026-04-24, the project
re-licensed to Apache-2.0. The rationale, including the conflict
between AGPL-on-the-library and default LangChain / LangGraph /
CrewAI / LlamaIndex / PydanticAI middleware bundling, is captured
in `docs/adr/0001-license-split.md` and references the strategy
documents in `docs/strategy/2026-04-mesh-review.md`.

The companion AgentMesh service (separate repository at
https://github.com/kenithphilip/AgentMesh) remains under
AGPL-3.0-or-later. The split mirrors the
Grafana / Mattermost / Plausible model: permissive license on
the library, copyleft on the service.

== Contribution policy ==

Contributions to this repository require a Developer Certificate
of Origin (DCO) sign-off. See CONTRIBUTING.md for details. The
DCO ensures all contributions are eligible for inclusion under
the Apache-2.0 license without requiring a CLA.

